<h2>Charleswood is a Place for Families to Call Home</h2>
<p>Located just east of the Crowchild Trail and the University of Calgary, Charleswood is a dream location for families at any stage. Charleswood is a place you can raise your children in, all the way from preschool to university and beyond.</p>
<p>As part of the Triwood Community Assosiciation, Charleswood families get exclusive access to amazing programs for kids, adults, and seniors. Programs include fitness for all ages, summer camps, public events, and exiciting yearly markets. The Triwood Arena hosts a variety of programming that include:</p>
<ul>
<li>hockey</li>
<li>ringette</li>
<li>soccer</li>
<li>broomball</li>
</ul>
<p>Programming also include 55+ social groups for both men and women, as well as active chapters of both Scouts and Girl Guides.</p>
</div>
</div>
