<h2>ABOUT CHARLESWOOD REAL ESTATE</h2>
<h3>Charlestown Style</h3>
<h4>Charlestown construction is solid.</h4>
<p>Featuring the mid-century craftsman homebuilding quality, you can still find the desirable original hardwood and plaster walls that so many yearn for today.</p>
<h4>The pride and care that Charlestown residents have is evident across each street and avenue.</h4>
<p>Homes that have already undergone renovations are really stunning. These renovations tend to work themselves from the inside out, so pay special attention to MLS&reg; listing pictures before you make up your mind. You could be missing out on your Calgary dream home otherwise!</p>
